Summary: it changed shape with white star looking lights moving slowly
divs: Sighting DetailsI walked outside the trailer of my boyfriends house and looked up to what at first looked like a cluster of little stars but then they moved and began twisting amongst itself . It moved very slowly. But it appeared to have a cloud cover or mist around it. It kept moving until it went to high for me to see anymore and then the 'stars' bust out n scattered n it was gone.
